  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Neutron-Rich Fuel Element",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "富中子燃料元素",
    "TencentChinese": "富中子燃料元素",
    "TraditionalChinese": "富中子燃料元素"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "Radioactive isotope commonly used to fuel the fusion reactor at the heart of starship <span class=\"name name-technology\">Pulse Engines</span>.<br><br>Abundant in interstellar asteroid fields, Tritium can be <span class=\"name name-commodity\">mined from asteroids</span> using starship weaponry. Scan (<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>) to search for <span class=\"name name-technology\">tritium-rich asteroids</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种放射性同位素，通常为飞船<span class=\"name name-technology\">脉冲驱动器</span>核心的聚变反应堆提供燃料。<br><br>星际小行星带内储量丰富，可使用飞船武器从<span class=\"name name-commodity\">从小行星上开采氚</span>。扫描（<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>）以搜寻<span class=\"name name-technology\">富含氚的小行星</span>。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种放射性同位素，通常为飞船<span class=\"name name-technology\">脉冲驱动器</span>核心的聚变反应堆提供燃料。<br><br>星际小行星带内储量丰富，可使用飞船武器从<span class=\"name name-commodity\">从小行星上开采</span>氚。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "輻射同位素，通常用來作為太空船<span class=\"name name-technology\">脈衝引擎</span>中心核融合反應器的燃料。<br><br>星際間的小行星帶可以找到大量氚，並用太空船武器<span class=\"name name-commodity\">從小行星中開採</span>。掃描 (<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>) 即可找尋<span class=\"name name-technology\">富含氚的小行星</span>。"
  },
